1040 REM ROOM 1
1050 PRINT"YOU ARE IN THE FORMER RECREATION"
1060 PRINT"CENTER. EQUIPMENT FOR MUSCLE-TRAINING"
1070 PRINT"IN ZERO GRAVITY LITTERS THE AREA"
1080 RETURN
