1242 PRINT"THE VIEW OF THE STARS FROM THIS OBSERVATION"
1245 PRINT"PLATFORM IS MAGNIFICENT, AS FAR AS THE EYE"
1246 PRINT"CAN SEE. THE SINGLE EXIT IS BACK WHERE YOU"
1250 PRINT"CAME FROM"
1260 RETURN
