1800 IF RND>0.5 THEN PRINT"YOUR BODY TWISTS AND BURNS..."
1810 PRINT"YOU ARE CAUGHT IN A DEADLY RADIATION FIELD"
1820 PRINT"SLOWLY YOU REALISE THIS IS THE END"
1830 IF RND>0.5 THEN PRINT"NO MATTER WHAT YOU DO"
1835 IF RND>0.5 THEN PRINT"YOU ARE DOOMED TO DIE HERE"
1840 RETURN
